## This is a template for world chunks used by WorldStreamer.
## Each chunk file is named chunk_X_Y.tscn where X,Y are chunk coordinates.
## WorldStreamer loads these dynamically: chunk_-1_0.tscn, chunk_1_2.tscn, etc.
##
## Chunk contents:
##   - TileMapLayer nodes for ground, walls, details
##   - Enemy spawn nodes (disabled until chunk is loaded)
##   - Prop/decoration nodes
##   - Interactables (chests, signs, etc.)
##
## To create new chunks:
##   1. Duplicate this file and rename: chunk_X_Y.tscn
##   2. Open in Godot editor
##   3. Paint tiles on the TileMapLayer nodes
##   4. Add enemies, NPCs, and interactables as children of Entities
##   5. Bake NavigationRegion2D if needed

